      <Value Culture="en-US"><![CDATA[{
  "contentData": [
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "bfc7ae19-ff25-49a3-9dcb-f402e80f177b",
      "key": "f6cb3219-3e79-42b2-9681-c304026bd2b1",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "eyebrow",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Our focus"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "A complete solution from design to <em>energy monetization</em>."
        },
        {
          "alias": "text",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "<p>From idea to profit. We bring together design, sales of <strong>BESS solutions</strong>, installation, operations and maintenance, legal and financial support, as well as integration into virtual power plants. In one place you get the complete expertise needed to make an energy project technically reliable, regulatory compliant, and <strong>maximally cost-effective</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "button",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            {
              "name": "Our solutions",
              "target": null,
              "unique": null,
              "type": null,
              "udi": null,
              "url": "#",
              "queryString": null,
              "culture": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "alias": "items",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "BESS solutions sales\nInstallation and commissioning\nOperations and maintenance (O&M)\nLegal and banking consulting\nEnergy law\nVPP - Virtual power plant"
        },
        {
          "alias": "overlay",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            {
              "key": "d7523ab5-b6eb-4bd3-bca1-f9f59456cf08",
              "mediaKey": "ff434fe5-ff30-41ba-94c2-c8ea47c6ee06",
              "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
              "crops": [],
              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "c0a7f3e1-2b4d-4f6a-8c1e-9d3b5a7e1f20",
      "key": "682517d6-6f71-48b3-8e13-fd6ba7426a1c",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "eyebrow",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Next step"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Talk to our <em>team</em>."
        },
        {
          "alias": "text",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "<p><strong data-start=\"516\" data-end=\"548\">Submit an inquiry via the form</strong><br>Provide basic information about the project, and our team will contact you with a proposed solution.</p><p data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"770\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><strong data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"675\">Response within 24 hours</strong><br>Once we receive your inquiry, you will get feedback and the next steps for realizing the project.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "formTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Send a message"
        },
        {
          "alias": "formSubtitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Our team will pick up your inquiry and respond within 24h."
        },
        {
          "alias": "recipients",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "maksimbogunovic@gmail.com"
        },
        {
          "alias": "backgroundColor",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            "Navy"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "b0c51460-6d98-44e8-8b81-22c4d2839082",
      "key": "b2876bc6-2d6f-4565-8f25-43eb732a7c19",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "eyebrow",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "SERVICES AND SUPPORT"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Support throughout your system's entire life cycle."
        },
        {
          "alias": "text",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "<p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">We understand that quality service and expert support are key to the long-term success of an energy storage system.</span><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Our team provides comprehensive technical expertise to ensure optimal performance, reliable operation, and a long service life for your BESS systems.</span><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">From planning and implementation to continuous monitoring and maintenance, we provide support tailored to the specific requirements of each project, with the goal of maximizing the value of your investment.</span></p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "button",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
